ype\", \"Authorization\"],\n  }),\n);\n\n// Request logging — correlate frontend fetch timing with server-side processing\napp.use(\"*\", async (c, next) => {","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_015guebxcpHhYbWYzaWhzX43","session_id":"04709d28-c77b-4687-bdb5-b2ffc1a1c744","uuid":"ac36ac65-94f7-42d3-b8be-8e6f1698eb80","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:03:16.647Z"}
